name: ipympl
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.0.3" %}
{% set sha256 = "979f034ffbdfafc189afad4b974ce1b90719a0ab9afdfbe886dd98c541f6f5fd" %}

package:
    name: ipympl
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: ipympl-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/i/ipympl/ipympl-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python
        - ipywidgets >=5.1.5
        - matplotlib >=2.0.0

test:
    imports:
        - ipympl

about:
    home: https://github.com/matplotlib/jupyter-matplotlib
    license: BSD 3-Clause
    summary: Matplotlib Jupyter Extension

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - JasonGrout
    - SylvainCorlay
    - tacaswell
